  {
    "hotel_id": "1346876",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/the-anam_4/hotel/nha-trang-vn.html",
    "name": "The Anam Cam Ranh",
    "detail": "Having travelled in Vietnam many times, staying in many different types of accomodation, as far as Resort accomodation goes we found this to be surely one of the best. Removed as it is from the ramshackle busyness of Nha Trang, The Anam provides a place of peaceful respite and relaxation. From the architecture and layout of the buildings and villas, the well-tended and green open spaces and gardens, the tasteful, elegant decor and attention to detail everywhere you look, it is beautiful in every respect. The villas have been planned and planted with surrounding gardens to ensure privacy and garden/lawn views down to the ocean. The private area of beach is excellent, with gentle waves, water just the perfect temperature and amazingly clean, safe and peaceful, with absolutely no buzzing or biting insects or pedlars to disturb the tranquility. Choice of three pools are all lovely, and there's an abundance of shade while meandering the various paths and buildings. ",
